      "content": "Here is a draft emphasizing the change: \"As we evolve, we're upgrading our concierge system to offer lightning-fast responses. While this new platform promises incredible speed, please know that our deep, nuanced level of personalized service—like crafting bespoke itineraries—is something we value immensely. During this transition, there may be a slight shift in how we capture those intricate details, and we appreciate your patience as we fine-tune the new experience to match the high standard you expect.\"",
